desc.en: LED (Enterprise Operation System) LED lighting license is the first application of lighting ecosystem in the blockchain technology in the world. Combined with the technical characteristics of the blockchain technology, such as untamable, it enables the energy saving lighting industry chain to achieve the information consensus of the upper, middle and lower reaches, creating the world's first energy saving lighting product real economy blockchain asset.
desc.zh: EOS (Enterprise Operation System) LED照明通证是目前世界首个打通照明生态圈在区块链技术应用,结合区块链技术的无法篡改等技术特点，让节能照明产业链实现上中下游的信息共识，打造了全球首个节能照明产品实体经济区块链资产。
